<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SITXFIN010 Section C — Assessment Roadmap</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy:   #1A2F4A;
    --teal:   #0D7A6E;
    --gold:   #D4A017;
    --req1:   #0D7A6E;
    --req2:   #B07030;
    --req3:   #6B3A8E;
    --req1-lt: #E8F4F0;
    --req2-lt: #FEF3E0;
    --req3-lt: #F3EDF9;
    --req1-mid:#B2DDD5;
    --req2-mid:#F0D8A0;
    --req3-mid:#D5BDE8;
    --bg:     #F0F3F7;
    --card:   #FFFFFF;
    --border: #D8E3EE;
    --text:   #1A2F4A;
    --muted:  #5A6E85;
    --done:   #1D7A4F;
  }

  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .header {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 28px 40px 22px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(26,47,74,0.25);
  }
  .header-left h1 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .header-left p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: #8EA9C4;
    margin-top: 3px;
  }
  .header-badge {
    background: var(--teal);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .progress-wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 14px;
  }
  .progress-bar-outer {
    flex: 1;
    height: 6px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .progress-bar-inner {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 6px;
    width: 0%;
    transition: width 0.5s ease;
  }
  .progress-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #8EA9C4;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* ── LAYOUT ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .board {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 32px 60px;
  }

  /* ── INTRO STRIP ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .intro {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-left: 5px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px 28px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .intro-icon { font-size: 2rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .intro-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--navy);
  }
  .intro-text p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .intro-pills {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .pill {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  }
  .pill-1 { background: var(--req1-lt); color: var(--req1); }
  .pill-2 { background: var(--req2-lt); color: var(--req2); }
  .pill-3 { background: var(--req3-lt); color: var(--req3); }

  /* ── SECTION COLUMNS ─────────────────────────────────────── */
  .columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* ── REQ COLUMN ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .req-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }

  .req-header {
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 22px;
    color: #fff;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .req-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px; right: -20px;
    width: 100px; height: 100px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }
  .req-1 .req-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D7A6E 0%, #0A5C53 100%); }
  .req-2 .req-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #B07030 0%, #8B5220 100%); }
  .req-3 .req-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B3A8E 0%, #4A2363 100%); }

  .req-number {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .req-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .req-header .req-desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    opacity: 0.88;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .req-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .req-meta span {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  }
  .req-steps-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0 4px;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  /* ── STEP CARD ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .step-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .step-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(26,47,74,0.1); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .step-card.done { opacity: 0.7; }
  .step-card.done .step-header { background: #F0FAF5 !important; }

  .step-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .step-card.open .step-header { border-bottom-color: var(--border); }

  .step-check {
    width: 26px; height: 26px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .req-1 .step-check { border-color: var(--req1-mid); color: var(--req1); }
  .req-2 .step-check { border-color: var(--req2-mid); color: var(--req2); }
  .req-3 .step-check { border-color: var(--req3-mid); color: var(--req3); }
  .step-check.checked { background: var(--done); border-color: var(--done); color: #fff; }

  .step-title-wrap { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .step-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .req-1 .step-label { color: var(--req1); }
  .req-2 .step-label { color: var(--req2); }
  .req-3 .step-label { color: var(--req3); }

  .step-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .step-chevron {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    transition: transform 0.25s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .step-card.open .step-chevron { transform: rotate(180deg); }

  /* ── STEP BODY ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .step-body {
    display: none;
    padding: 16px;
    background: #FAFCFE;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .step-card.open .step-body { display: flex; }

  .what-box {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
  }
  .what-box h4 {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 7px;
  }
  .what-box p {
    font-size: 0.83rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .tab-ref {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .tab-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  }
  .tab-tag.t-assum { background: #E8F0FA; color: #1A4A8B; }
  .tab-tag.t-budget { background: #E8F4F0; color: #0D5C50; }
  .tab-tag.t-monthly { background: #EFF5FE; color: #2855A0; }
  .tab-tag.t-review { background: #FEF3E8; color: #8B4A10; }
  .tab-tag.t-dash { background: #F3EDF9; color: #5A2880; }
  .tab-tag.t-instr { background: #FEF9E8; color: #7A5A00; }

  .how-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .how-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .how-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .req-1 .how-list li::before { color: var(--req1); }
  .req-2 .how-list li::before { color: var(--req2); }
  .req-3 .how-list li::before { color: var(--req3); }

  .tip-box {
    border-radius: 7px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .tip-box.tip-warn { background: #FFF3E0; border-left: 3px solid #E08000; color: #5C3800; }
  .tip-box.tip-info { background: var(--req1-lt); border-left: 3px solid var(--req1); color: #0A4A42; }
  .tip-box.tip-key  { background: var(--req2-lt); border-left: 3px solid var(--req2); color: #5C3800; }
  .tip-box.tip-note { background: var(--req3-lt); border-left: 3px solid var(--req3); color: #3A1A5C; }

  .mark-done-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 7px 14px;
    border-radius: 7px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .req-1 .mark-done-btn { background: var(--req1); color: #fff; }
  .req-2 .mark-done-btn { background: var(--req2); color: #fff; }
  .req-3 .mark-done-btn { background: var(--req3); color: #fff; }
  .mark-done-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; transform: scale(1.02); }
  .mark-done-btn.undone { background: #e5e8ec; color: var(--muted); }

  /* ── CONNECTOR ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .connector-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin: 36px 0 12px;
  }
  .connector-line {
    height: 3px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .conn-1 { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--req1) 0%, transparent 100%); }
  .conn-2 { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--req2) 0%, transparent 100%); }
  .conn-3 { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--req3) 0%, transparent 100%); }

  /* ── SUMMARY STRIP ───────────────────────────────────────── */
  .summary-strip {
    background: var(--navy);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    margin-top: 36px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .sum-item { text-align: center; }
  .sum-number {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .sum-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #8EA9C4;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .sum-divider {
    width: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    margin: 0 10px;
  }

  /* ── LEGEND ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .legend {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .legend-dot {
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .columns, .connector-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .summary-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .board { padding: 20px 16px 48px; }
    .header { padding: 18px 20px; }
  }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @keyframes fadeSlideIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .req-col { animation: fadeSlideIn 0.5s ease both; }
  .req-col:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .req-col:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.22s; }
  .req-col:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.34s; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── HEADER ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<header class="header">
  <div style="flex:1">
    <div class="header-left">
      <h1>SITXFIN010 — Section C Assessment Roadmap</h1>
      <p>Prepare and Monitor Budgets  ·  Le' Culinaire Hospitality Institute  ·  RTO 45326</p>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-wrap">
      <div class="progress-bar-outer"><div class="progress-bar-inner" id="progressBar"></div></div>
      <span class="progress-label" id="progressLabel">0 of 14 completed</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="header-badge">Section C</div>
</header>

<!-- ── BOARD ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<main class="board">

  <!-- Intro -->
  <div class="intro">
    <div class="intro-icon">🗺️</div>
    <div class="intro-text">
      <h2>How to use this board</h2>
      <p>The Section C performance activity has <strong>3 assessment requirements</strong>. Each column below is one requirement. Click any card to see exactly <em>what</em> to do, <em>which tab</em> of your Excel workbook to use, and <em>how</em> to write your response in the Student Guide. Tick each step as you complete it to track your progress.</p>
      <div class="intro-pills">
        <span class="pill pill-1">✦ Req 1 — Prepare the Budget (Part 1 A–J)</span>
        <span class="pill pill-2">✦ Req 2 — Decision Report (Part 2)</span>
        <span class="pill pill-3">✦ Req 3 — Monitor &amp; Review (Part 3 Meetings 1–3)</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Three columns -->
  <div class="columns">

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- REQUIREMENT 1 -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="req-col req-1">
      <div class="req-header">
        <div class="req-number">ASSESSMENT REQUIREMENT 1</div>
        <h2>Prepare a Draft &amp; Final Budget for the Next Two Financial Quarters</h2>
        <p class="req-desc">In consultation with the accounts department — demonstrating consultation, factor analysis, and draft/final versions within designated timelines.</p>
        <div class="req-meta">
          <span>📋 Part 1 of Student Guide</span>
          <span>Sections A → J</span>
          <span>10 steps</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="req-steps-label">Steps to complete →</p>

      <!-- A: Business Context -->
      <div class="step-card" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
        <div class="step-header">
          <div class="step-check" onclick="toggleCheck(event, this)"></div>
          <div class="step-title-wrap">
            <div class="step-label">Section A</div>
            <div class="step-title">Set Your Business Context</div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-chevron">▼</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <div class="what-box"><h4>What the assessment requires</h4><p>Describe the business you are budgeting for — its type, what the budget covers (sales, food, wages, overheads), and the budget period (Q1 and Q2 dates).</p></div>
          <div class="tab-ref">
            <span class="tab-tag t-instr">📋 Instructions Tab</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="how-list">
            <li>Open the Instructions tab in your Excel workbook</li>
            <li>Use your restaurant name, cuisine type and budget period</li>
            <li>Write 3–5 sentences: what is the business, what does the budget cover, and what are the two quarter dates</li>
            <li>In the Student Guide, fill in the ✏️ YOUR RESPONSE box in Section A</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tip-box tip-info">💡 <span>Do not use the trainer's example restaurant. Your response must describe YOUR restaurant from the Instructions tab.</span></div>
          <button class="mark-done-btn" onclick="markDone(event, this)">✓ Mark as Done</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- B: Consultation -->
      <div class="step-card" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
        <div class="step-header">
          <div class="step-check" onclick="toggleCheck(event, this)"></div>
          <div class="step-title-wrap">
            <div class="step-label">Section B</div>
            <div class="step-title">Consultation Process</div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-chevron">▼</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <div class="what-box"><h4>What the assessment requires</h4><p>Consult relevant parties before preparing your budget. Name at least 3 people or roles you consulted and explain what you discussed with each one.</p></div>
          <div class="tab-ref">
            <span class="tab-tag t-assum">⚙️ Assumptions Tab</span>
            <span class="tab-tag t-budget">💰 Budget_Q1_Q2 Tab</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="how-list">
            <li>Name at least 3 people: e.g. Accounts Officer, Head Chef, Restaurant Supervisor</li>
            <li>For each person, write 2–3 sentences: what did you ask them, what did they tell you</li>
            <li>Connect each consultation to a specific figure in your Assumptions tab (e.g. "The Head Chef recommended a food cost of 33% — I entered this in cell C23 of the Assumptions tab")</li>
            <li>Fill in Section B of the Student Guide</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tip-box tip-warn">⚠️ <span>Generic responses like "I consulted staff" will not meet the standard. Name who, what they said, and where you applied their advice in your workbook.</span></div>
          <button class="mark-done-btn" onclick="markDone(event, this)">✓ Mark as Done</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- C: Data -->
      <div class="step-card" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
        <div class="step-header">
          <div class="step-check" onclick="toggleCheck(event, this)"></div>
          <div class="step-title-wrap">
            <div class="step-label">Section C</div>
            <div class="step-title">Data Identified, Accessed &amp; Interpreted</div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-chevron">▼</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <div class="what-box"><h4>What the assessment requires</h4><p>Identify what data you used, where you got it from, and what it told you. This is your evidence that you analysed real information before entering numbers into the workbook.</p></div>
          <div class="tab-ref">
            <span class="tab-tag t-assum">⚙️ Assumptions Tab</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="how-list">
            <li>List the data sources you used: previous sales records, supplier price lists, payroll records, utility bills, booking data, food cost reports</li>
            <li>For each source, explain how it informed a specific figure in your Assumptions tab (e.g. "Supplier quotes informed my food cost % — I set 33% in cell C23")</li>
            <li>Write 4–6 sentences describing what the data revealed and how it changed your estimates</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="mark-done-btn" onclick="markDone(event, this)">✓ Mark as Done</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- D: Factors -->
      <div class="step-card" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
        <div class="step-header">
          <div class="step-check" onclick="toggleCheck(event, this)"></div>
          <div class="step-title-wrap">
            <div class="step-label">Section D</div>
            <div class="step-title">Internal &amp; External Factors</div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-chevron">▼</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <div class="what-box"><h4>What the assessment requires</h4><p>Identify the factors with the most potential to influence income and expenditure — both inside the business (internal) and outside (external). Each factor must connect to a specific workbook decision.</p></div>
          <div class="tab-ref">
            <span class="tab-tag t-assum">⚙️ Assumptions Tab</span>
            <span class="tab-tag t-budget">💰 Budget_Q1_Q2 Tab</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="how-list">
            <li><strong>Internal:</strong> Labour costs (Labour Planner), organisational objectives (Budget tab rows 30–34), planned promotions (Marketing line)</li>
            <li><strong>External:</strong> Commodity prices (food cost % in Assumptions cell C23), economic conditions (conservative Q1 vs Q2 revenue), market trends (marketing budget increase)</li>
            <li>For each factor, write the specific figure from your workbook that reflects it</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="mark-done-btn" onclick="markDone(event, this)">✓ Mark as Done</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- E: Authorities -->
      <div class="step-card" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
        <div class="step-header">
          <div class="step-check" onclick="toggleCheck(event, this)"></div>
